    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">AI Chat System - Master Audit & Implementation Status</h1>
    <h2 style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large); margin-top: 0;">Comprehensive Consolidation of AI Chat Documentation</h2>
    
    <div class="last-updated" style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
        Created: 2026-01-06 05:15 UTC | 
        Version: 0.01 (Master Index) | 
        Status: Phase 1 COMPLETE, Phases 2-4 PLANNED | 
        Consolidates: 7 existing documentation files + codebase scan + status tracking
    </div>

    <!-- QUICK NAVIGATION -->
    <div style="background: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
        <h3 style="color: #1976d2; margin-top: 0;">📋 Quick Navigation (Jump to Section)</h3>
        <ul style="margin: 10px 0; color: #1976d2;">
            <li><a href="#executive-summary" style="color: #2196f3; text-decoration: none;">Executive Summary</a> - Current status snapshot</li>
            <li><a href="#phase-status" style="color: #2196f3; text-decoration: none;">Phase Implementation Status</a> - What's done, what's planned</li>
            <li><a href="#files-involved" style="color: #2196f3; text-decoration: none;">All Files Involved</a> - Code, documentation, models</li>
            <li><a href="#feature-requirements" style="color: #2196f3; text-decoration: none;">Feature Requirements Matrix</a> - 12 requirements breakdown</li>
            <li><a href="#database-schema" style="color: #2196f3; text-decoration: none;">Database Tables</a> - 6 tables with field definitions</li>
            <li><a href="#documentation-index" style="color: #2196f3; text-decoration: none;">Documentation Index</a> - Map of 7+ docs</li>
            <li><a href="#implementation-timeline" style="color: #2196f3; text-decoration: none;">Implementation Timeline</a> - Phases 2-5 schedule</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- EXECUTIVE SUMMARY -->
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2 id="executive-summary" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">1. Executive Summary</h2>
        
        <div style="background: #d4edda; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #155724;">✅ Current Status: Phase 1 COMPLETE</h3>
            <p style="color: #155724; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Database & Model Layer:</strong> All 6 Result classes created, tables initialized at startup, automated in production</p>
            <p style="color: #155724; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Timeline:</strong> Phase 1 complete (Dec 25, 2025), Phases 2-5 planned for 8-10 weeks starting Jan 2026</p>
            <p style="color: #155724; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Scope:</strong> Intelligent AI Chat widget with doc search, code search, web search, role-based access, multi-model support, conversation resume, Grok API integration, admin controls</p>
        </div>

        <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">The AI Chat System</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">Comserv is implementing an advanced AI Chat system that enables users to:</p>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
            <li><strong>Chat Widget:</strong> Access AI in lower-right corner (visible to all users)</li>
            <li><strong>Documentation Search:</strong> AI automatically searches /Documentation/ metadata index</li>
            <li><strong>Code Search:</strong> Developers/admins can search application source code</li>
            <li><strong>Web Search:</strong> Optional web search with admin verification workflow</li>
            <li><strong>Multi-Model:</strong> Ollama (all users), XAI/Grok (dev/admin)</li>
            <li><strong>Role-Based:</strong> Users only see documentation they have permission to access</li>
            <li><strong>Conversation Resume:</strong> Users can search past conversations and resume with full context</li>
            <li><strong>Audit Trail:</strong> All Q&A logged with user, timestamp, model, sources</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Two Chat Systems in Comserv</h3>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <div style="background: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #155724;">✅ AI Chat (Modern)</h4>
                <p style="color: #155724; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Status:</strong> Implemented & active</p>
                <p style="color: #155724; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Tables:</strong> ai_conversations, ai_messages</p>
                <p style="color: #155724; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Controller:</strong> Comserv::Controller::AI</p>
                <p style="color: #155724; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Models:</strong> Full ORM, relationships working</p>
                <p style="color: #155724; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Data Persistence:</strong> ✅ Working</p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">⚠️ Basic Chat (Legacy)</h4>
                <p style="color: #856404; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Status:</strong> Implemented but no ORM</p>
                <p style="color: #856404; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Table:</strong> chat_messages</p>
                <p style="color: #856404; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Controller:</strong> Comserv::Controller::Chat</p>
                <p style="color: #856404; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Models:</strong> ❌ Missing ORM model</p>
                <p style="color: #856404; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Data Access:</strong> Raw SQL queries</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

