                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Admin model/agent config (dynamic)</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center;">🟠 High</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center;">4</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center;">Admin</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">FR-12</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Grok API integration (encrypted keys)</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center;">🟠 High</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center;">2</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center;">Config</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <div style="background: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1976d2;">📊 Requirement Summary</h4>
            <p style="color: #1976d2; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>4 Critical (FR-1 to FR-4):</strong> Core widget functionality, documentation search, role-based filtering, audit logging</p>
            <p style="color: #1976d2; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>8 High (FR-5 to FR-12):</strong> Advanced features including model selection, web/code search, conversation resume, Grok API, admin controls</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DATABASE SCHEMA -->
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2 id="database-schema" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">5. Database Tables & Schema</h2>
        
        <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">6 Tables Created / Extended</h4>
            <p style="color: #666; margin: 5px 0; font-size: 13px;">All stored in <code>ENCY</code> database. Auto-initialized via DBIx::Class schema on startup.</p>
        </div>

        <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">1. ai_messages (Extended)</h4>
        <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 10px 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; overflow-x: auto;">
            <strong>Primary Key:</strong> id<br>
            <strong>New Fields:</strong> agent_type, model_used, search_context (json), sources_cited (json), user_role, response_time_ms, tokens_used, is_verified
        </div>

        <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">2. documentation_metadata_index (New)</h4>
        <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 10px 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; overflow-x: auto;">
            <strong>Purpose:</strong> Metadata + searchable excerpts of .tt files (full content stays on disk)<br>
            <strong>Key Fields:</strong> file_path (UNIQUE), title, searchable_text (FULLTEXT), content_hash, role_access (json), last_file_modified
        </div>

        <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">3. code_search_index (New)</h4>
        <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 10px 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; overflow-x: auto;">
            <strong>Purpose:</strong> Index of .pm and .tt code for developer/admin search<br>
            <strong>Key Fields:</strong> file_path (UNIQUE), code_elements (json - functions/classes/line_numbers), searchable_code (FULLTEXT), min_role
        </div>

        <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">4. web_search_results (New)</h4>
        <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 10px 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; overflow-x: auto;">
            <strong>Purpose:</strong> Stores unverified web search results (before admin approval)<br>
            <strong>Key Fields:</strong> query, result_url, is_verified (boolean), verified_by_user_id, used_in_ai_message_id
        </div>

        <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">5. ai_model_config (New)</h4>
        <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 10px 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; overflow-x: auto;">
            <strong>Purpose:</strong> Admin configuration for model access by role<br>
            <strong>Key Fields:</strong> role, agent_type, model_name, api_endpoint, api_key_encrypted, enabled, priority
        </div>

        <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">6. documentation_role_access (New)</h4>
        <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 10px 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; overflow-x: auto;">
            <strong>Purpose:</strong> Fine-grained role-based access to documentation sections<br>
            <strong>Key Fields:</strong> role, doc_section_pattern (e.g., 'admin/*'), can_access (boolean)
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DOCUMENTATION INDEX -->
