    <!-- IMPLEMENTATION TIMELINE -->
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2 id="implementation-timeline" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">7. Implementation Timeline (Phases 2-5)</h2>
        
        <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Total Duration: 8-10 weeks (Jan 8 → Mar 1, 2026)</h4>
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 13px; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Note:</strong> Phase 1 (Database & Model Layer) is already complete. Phases 2-5 begin Jan 8 and run in sequence.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 3fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;">
                    <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">Phase 2 (Backend)</h4>
                    <p style="color: #856404; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-3 weeks</p>
                    <p style="color: #856404; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Start:</strong> Jan 8-15</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #f0f8f4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #333;"><strong>Services to implement:</strong></p>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; color: #333; font-size: 13px;">
                        <li>DocumentationIndexer (scan .tt files, build metadata index)</li>
                        <li>LLMOllama service (local model via API)</li>
                        <li>LLMXAI service (encrypted API key management)</li>
                        <li>LLMGrok service (Grok API integration)</li>
                        <li>Extend AI controller with search/response logic</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 3fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div style="background: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;">
                    <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1976d2;">Phase 3 (Frontend)</h4>
                    <p style="color: #1976d2; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-3 weeks</p>
                    <p style="color: #1976d2; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Start:</strong> Jan 15+</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #f0f8f4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #333;"><strong>UI to implement:</strong></p>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; color: #333; font-size: 13px;">
                        <li>Chat widget HTML/CSS (theme-compatible, Grok.ai aesthetic)</li>
                        <li>JavaScript message handling + model selector dropdown</li>
                        <li>/ai/conversations page (search, filter, resume conversation)</li>
                        <li>Inject widget on all pages</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 3fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div style="background: #f3e5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #7b1fa2;">
                    <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #7b1fa2;">Phase 4 (Admin)</h4>
                    <p style="color: #7b1fa2; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-3 weeks</p>
                    <p style="color: #7b1fa2; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Start:</strong> Jan 22+</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #f0f8f4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #333;"><strong>Admin features:</strong></p>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; color: #333; font-size: 13px;">
                        <li>Model configuration UI (enable/disable per role)</li>
                        <li>Agent configuration (enable/disable agents, default models)</li>
                        <li>Grok API key management (encrypted storage)</li>
                        <li>Web search approval workflow dashboard</li>
                        <li>Analytics dashboard (usage, performance, errors)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 3fr; gap: 20px;">
                <div style="background: #fce4ec; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #c2185b;">
